# Kalite Kapıları

## Test Coverage (MVP-0)

| Alan | Line hedef | Not |
|------|------------|-----|
| Auth + RBAC | ≥%90 | Bypass senaryoları zorunlu |
| Processor pipeline | ≥%80 | dedup, normalize, score |
| Collector parse | ≥%70 | Dış kaynak format hataları |
| AI engine (parse, prompt) | ≥%70 | LLM mock ile |
| API router | ≥%60 | Validation + guard |
| Repository | ≥%50 | Karmaşık sorgular öncelikli |

**CI gate:** PR'da coverage düşerse merge engellenir (fail-under=70 genel).

## CI Pipeline (PR Zorunlu)

`Docs/09_DEV_WORKFLOW.md` §5.1 — `.github/workflows/test.yml`: ruff → mypy → pytest unit → pytest integration (PostgreSQL service) → coverage report (fail-under=70).

Security-sensitive değişiklik → ek reviewer.

## Python / TypeScript

- `mypy` strict; `any` ve `# type: ignore` review red
- `ruff` format + lint green
- Shared tipler `packages/shared/` — FE/BE duplicate schema yasak

## Frontend Kalite

- Lighthouse (MVP-1+): performance ≥80, a11y ≥90
- Next.js bundle: initial route JS makul tutulur (<200 KB gzipped hedef)
- `localStorage` token yasak
- Web Vitals: LCP < 2.5s, CLS < 0.1

## API Performans Hedefleri

- Dashboard API p95 < 500 ms
- Chatbot yanıt p95 < 10 s (LLM dahil)

## E2E

MVP-0'da kapsam dışı. MVP-1'de Playwright değerlendirilir.

